Class DateEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • DateEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Event, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReminderEvent, UrgentEvent

    public class DateEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, Event
    DateEvent is the main type of object stored in the EventList (can store others). Holds information of an event.
    Author:
    Timothy Nguyen, Andy Wu, William Luna
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
